ygData.messageBody:
If I quit, I will sell it off for 2 reasons:
1. To recover my usage fee so far. I wanna enjoy the game FOC whenever
possible, and earn abit for sacrifacing my time for my sleep, heh.
2. It's really a waste to terminate an acct with high lvl wiz, afterall it
took me several months to achieve it. I will rather sell it and let
someone else to con't playing it.

You've come up with a nice idea, using wiz to camp for item and earn RL
money. My main purpose of play games is to enjoy it instead of making
money. If it doesn't take up much time to use ya method to earn some quick
buck, I will give it a try. But if it required days of camping like Jboot,
I will rather spend time playing UO, hehe.

Ziltus
